```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many soles of a hamster's foot are facing the camera?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many soles of a hamster's foot are facing the camera?')

FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
